org.jetel.util

Class JetelVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.util.JetelVersion

  • public final class JetelVersion
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which carries information about current CloverETL library version (both major & minor).
    Can be used to check for compatibility.
    Values are automatically updated by ANT build file when release is built.
    Since:
    25.10.2005
